    "causal_summary": "The presentation/router split placed each command's display contract in `.opencode/commands/<family>/assets/<name>_presentation.md`. The command loader discovers every `.md` under `.opencode/commands/` recursively (and `.claude/commands` symlinks to the same tree), so all 24 presentation assets registered as bogus slash commands, polluting the namespace.",
